column3: As once did this very realm we call home, from the darkest depths of unseemly ugliness shall you rise anew. Prepare yourself!
While customizing your hairstyle, you will be unable to communicate with players and engage in other activities.
Commencing the customization process will automatically cancel your Duty Finder registration.
Where once stood a disheveled shell of a <If(PlayerParameter(4))>woman<Else/>man</If>, there now shines...a beauty reborn.
When your star begins to dim, you need only send for Jandelaine. Till we meet again!
